<i>noun</i>: 태업 [태업], 둔화 [둔ː화] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>태업 [태업]</dt><br>
<dd>1. working lazily</dd><br>
<dd>일이나 공부를 게을리함.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of working or studying lazily.</dd><br>
<dd>2. slowdown; going slow</dd><br>
<dd>노동 분쟁 과정에서 일부러 일을 게을리하여 사용자에게 손해를 줌.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of intentionally working slowly in the process of a labor dispute, to cause damage to an employer.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>둔화 [둔ː화]</dt><br>
<dd>slowdown</dd><br>
<dd>반응이나 진행 속도가 느려짐.</dd><br>
<dd>Slowing of progress or the reaction to something.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>